Name:                repa
Version:             1.0.0.0
License:             MIT
License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              The DPH Team
Maintainer:          ndp@cse.unsw.edu.au
Build-Type:          Simple
Cabal-Version:       >=1.6
Stability:           experimental
Category:            Data Structures
Homepage:            http://trac.haskell.org/repa
